g.text: UML Diagram: Class DataSet in Context
- Move the mouse cursor over a name to see more information.
- Click on a name to go to the corresponding page.
- The arrows of the inheritance tree are

a.title: ― DataPoint: Container for an instance value.
a.xlink:title: ― DataPoint: Container for an instance value.

a.title: ― DataStructure: Data organization based on reusable data structure components.
a.xlink:title: ― DataStructure: Data organization based on reusable data structure components.

a.title: ― Key: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a dataset.
a.xlink:title: ― Key: Collection of data instances that uniquely identify a collection of data points in a dataset.

a.title: ― CatalogDetails: A set of information useful for attribution, data discovery, and access.
a.xlink:title: ― CatalogDetails: A set of information useful for attribution, data discovery, and access.

a.title: ― Identifier: Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.
a.xlink:title: ― Identifier: Identifier for objects requiring short- or long-lasting referencing and management.

a.title: ― KeyValueDataStore: Organized collection of key-value data. It is structured by a key value structure.
a.xlink:title: ― KeyValueDataStore: Organized collection of key-value data. It is structured by a key value structure.

a.title: ― DimensionalDataSet: Organized collection of multidimensional data. It is structured by a dimensional data structure.
a.xlink:title: ― DimensionalDataSet: Organized collection of multidimensional data. It is structured by a dimensional data structure.

a.title: ― WideDataSet: Organized collection of wide data. It is structured by a wide data structure.
a.xlink:title: ― WideDataSet: Organized collection of wide data. It is structured by a wide data structure.

a.title: ― LongDataSet: Organized collection of long data. It is structured by a long data structure.
a.xlink:title: ― LongDataSet: Organized collection of long data. It is structured by a long data structure.
